===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#Any of a series of [[carbohydrate]]s that are used by [[organism]]s to store energy.
#General term for [[sucrose]], [[glucose]], [[fructose]], etc.
# {{slang}} A [[kiss]].
#: ''(related) see also'' [[sugartime]] 
# An affectionate nickname for one of the opposite sex.
#:''I'll be with you in a moment, '''sugar'''.'' 
#{{context|US|slang}} Effemininity in a male, often implying [[homosexuality]]; primarily U.S. southern.
#: ''I think John has a little bit of '''sugar''' in him''

